data.description: PRICED TO SELL & only three years old!! Gorgeous four bedroom, two and a half bath home in the beautiful community of Parkview Hills is located only 25 minutes from Downtown Fort Worth and only 10 minutes from Eagle Mountain Lake! Home has been meticulously maintained and offers an open kitchen and living room concept with an oversized island, granite countertops, built in microwave, stainless-steel appliances, a huge bonus room and half bath upstairs as well as four large bedrooms with walk in closets, a private laundry room and a master suite with a private spa inspired bath all on the first level!  Exterior features include a huge corner lot with an oversized backyard with covered patio, privacy fence, sprinkler system and solar panels to help with those summer electric bills! Schedule your tour today and make this beauty your new home in 2024! Refrigerator and furnishings are all negotiable!
